-- Metalloinvest Signs $340 Million Iron Deal With Siemens, Midrex
-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 2012-08-31T12:20:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-31/metalloinvest-signs-340-million-iron-deal-with-siemens-midrex.html
Metalloinvest Holding,  Russia ’s
largest iron-ore producer, signed a 270 million euro ($340
million) contract with  Siemens AG (SIE)  and Midrex Technologies Inc.
for the expansion of hot briquetted iron output in the nation.  Siemens and Miderex will help Metalloinvest to increase its
production at the Lebedinsky mine in Central Russia with the
construction of a new 1.8 million metric ton-capacity plant, the
world’s largest, the companies said today in a joint statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
